sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Open channel details
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/workspaces/{workspaceId}/channels/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and workspace access
    API->>DB: Load channel details
    DB-->>API: Channel found
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + channel
    Frontend-->>User: Display channel header and metadata
